<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Switch to vim</title><link>http://switchtovimcom/</link><description>VIM </description><atom:link href="http://switchtovimcom/rss.xml" type="application/rss+xml" rel="self"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 30 Jul 2014 21:48:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola &lt;http://getnikola.com/&gt;</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>text processing</title><link>http://switchtovimcom/posts/text-processing.html</link><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tip: if you see capital letter you must press &lt;kbd&gt;SHIFT&lt;/kbd&gt;
Mode legend:
&lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="label label-primary"&gt;Insert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;i&lt;/kbd&gt; - enter insert mode and place cursor at current position
   &lt;span class="label label-primary"&gt;Insert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;I&lt;/kbd&gt; - enter insert mode and place cursor at start of the line
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;a&lt;/kbd&gt; - enter insert mode and place cursor after current position
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;A&lt;/kbd&gt; - enter insert mode and place cursor at the end of line
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;e&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;a&lt;/kbd&gt; - enter insert mode and place cursor at the end of line
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;J&lt;/kbd&gt; - join line below with current one
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;cc&lt;/kbd&gt; - change replace entire line
&lt;kbd&gt;S&lt;/kbd&gt; - change replace entire line
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;cw&lt;/kbd&gt; - change replace to  the end of word
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;c$&lt;/kbd&gt; - change replace to the end of line
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;d$&lt;/kbd&gt; - delete after cursor
&lt;kbd&gt;D&lt;/kbd&gt; - delete after cursor
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;u&lt;/kbd&gt; - undo
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;r&lt;/kbd&gt; - redo
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;.&lt;/kbd&gt; repeat last command
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul class="simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><guid>http://switchtovimcom/posts/text-processing.html</guid><pubDate>Mon, 21 Jul 2014 23:10:17 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Operations on file</title><link>http://switchtovimcom/posts/operations-on-file.html</link><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tip: if you see capital letter you must press &lt;kbd&gt;SHIFT&lt;/kbd&gt;
Mode legend:
&lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="label label-primary"&gt;Insert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ZZ&lt;/kbd&gt; - Save and quit
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;q&lt;/kbd&gt; - save and quit
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;is the same as &lt;br&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;q&lt;/kbd&gt; - save and exit
   &lt;span class="label label-info"&gt;Command line &lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;
but to avoid mistakes I will give examples in normal mode
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;q&lt;/kbd&gt; quit editing file
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;q!&lt;/kbd&gt; quit without changes
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;e&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;.&lt;/kbd&gt; directory explorer
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;n&lt;/kbd&gt; - edit new file
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;n!&lt;/kbd&gt; - edit new file without saving current changes
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;split&lt;/kbd&gt; filename - split window and load file
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;sview&lt;/kbd&gt; filename - split window and load file readonly
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><guid>http://switchtovimcom/posts/operations-on-file.html</guid><pubDate>Mon, 21 Jul 2014 22:07:36 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>movement</title><link>http://switchtovimcom/posts/movement.html</link><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Mode legend:
   &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class="label label-primary"&gt;Insert&lt;/span&gt;
Tip: if you see capital letter you must press SHIFT :)
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt; - next word by punctation    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image20" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/w.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;W&lt;/kbd&gt; - next word by spaces    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image21" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/W.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;b&lt;/kbd&gt; - back word by punctation    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;B&lt;/kbd&gt; - back word by spaces    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;e&lt;/kbd&gt; - next word set cursor at the end word by punctation    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image10" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/e.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;E&lt;/kbd&gt; - next word set cursor at the end word by spaces    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image11" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/E.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;h&lt;/kbd&gt; - move left  &lt;kbd&gt;l&lt;/kbd&gt; - move right  &lt;kbd&gt;k&lt;/kbd&gt; - move up  &lt;kbd&gt;j&lt;/kbd&gt; - move down    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image3" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/hlkj.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;:&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;3&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;8&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;Enter&lt;/kbd&gt; - go to 38th line    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="image38" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/38line.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;^&lt;/kbd&gt; - first non-blank character of line    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;)&lt;/kbd&gt; - zero) start of line    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;$&lt;/kbd&gt; - end of line    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;G&lt;/kbd&gt; - Go To command (prefix with number 4j moves down 4 lines.    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Windows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;Ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt; - swith between windows    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="imagecww" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/cww.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;Ctrl &lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w &lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;⇧&lt;/kbd&gt; - move cursor up a window example using ctr ww and ctr w arrows in example before switching windows ESC was pressed to enter &lt;b&gt;normal&lt;/b&gt; mode:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="imagecwa" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/cwarrow.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl &lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;+&lt;/kbd&gt; - increase size of current window    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="imagecwp" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/cw+.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;-&lt;/kbd&gt; - decrease size of current window    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="imagecwm" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/cw-.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;_&lt;/kbd&gt; - maximize current window    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="imagecwmax" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/cw_.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;=&lt;/kbd&gt; -  make all equal size    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="imagecwe" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/cw=.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;1&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;0&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;+&lt;/kbd&gt; - increase window size by 10 lines    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;vsplit file&lt;/kbd&gt; - vertical split
   &lt;span class="label label-info"&gt;Command line&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;sview&lt;/kbd&gt; - same as split, but readonly
   &lt;span class="label label-info"&gt;Command line&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;hide&lt;/kbd&gt; - close current window
   &lt;span class="label label-info"&gt;Command line&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;only&lt;/kbd&gt; - keep only this window open
   &lt;span class="label label-info"&gt;Command line &lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="imageonly" src="http://switchtovimcom/images/only.gif"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ls&lt;/kbd&gt; - show current buffers
   &lt;span class="label label-info"&gt;Command line &lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;b 2&lt;/kbd&gt; - open buffer #2 in this window
   &lt;span class="label label-info"&gt;Command line&lt;/span&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;W&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;s&lt;/kbd&gt; - split window horizontally    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;W&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;v&lt;/kbd&gt; - split window vertically    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;kbd&gt;ctrl&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;w&lt;/kbd&gt;&lt;kbd&gt;q&lt;/kbd&gt; - close window    &lt;span class="label label-success"&gt;Normal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr class="docutils"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><guid>http://switchtovimcom/posts/movement.html</guid><pubDate>Sat, 12 Jul 2014 20:18:32 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>